    adversary_description: >
      Emulation of a Lazarus Group attack graph using a trojanized Notepad++
      ComparePlus plugin DLL executed via Rundll32, followed by process injection,
      WMI lateral movement, registry/SAM credential dumping, scheduled task
      persistence, and network discovery with a custom SiteShooter tool.
